projects.projectDescription: As the Computer Science Project Lead, we collaborated with Johnson & Johnson Innovations on a grant connected to Rutgers Data Science Consulting. Our goal was to develop a system for generating survey results in PDF format for innovators who have taken the Health Equity Assessment Tool survey. My role on the project was to design a mockup of the report, develop the system for generating the personalized reports, and push the new PDF reports to J&J Innovationâ€™s server via SFTP.

GammaBets was a website for players who played the videogame Rust to play mini-games against other players and trade items in the videogame with other players. As the Lead Developer of the project, my task was to build the backend system that managed the mini-games, trades, transactions, etc. along with designing the frontend of the website from a mockup.
